	chapter.73239E8DB41DFA66.title: "Hitos de la Temporada"
	quest.0331AC0315EBB66D.quest_desc: ["Nestled among the trees, this lively tavern is usually a haven for villagers looking to unwind. Yet when the ale flows too freely, even the most peaceful patrons turn aggressive, defending their pub with surprising ferocity. Enter carefully or risk being caught in a drunken brawl."]
	quest.0331AC0315EBB66D.quest_subtitle: "Find a Greenwood Pub"
	quest.041A1C64A8468087.quest_desc: ["Suspended high in the sky, this arrowhead-shaped airship drifts on a massive aft propeller. Boarding is perilous, but those who succeed will witness its strange and fearsome inhabitants riding boar-like beasts, their eyeless faces obscured by ominous cages. Danger and mystery ride with them across the clouds."]
	quest.041A1C64A8468087.quest_subtitle: "Find a Heavenly Rider"
	quest.0B89EB36AC565461.quest_desc: ["Deep within this subterranean city, the heat of molten lava and the hum of industry dominate the air. The Netherâ€™s influence is strong here, fueling forges and animating Forge Sentinels that patrol every corridor. Only those prepared for fire and steel will survive, and claim the treasures forged within."]
	quest.0B89EB36AC565461.quest_subtitle: "Find a Foundry"
	quest.0CE50A7F4F1A0E4D.quest_desc: ["ladder stretches skyward, disappearing into the clouds. At its top floats a strange, floating vessel. What secrets or dangers await above, none can sayâ€¦ except that the view alone is enough to make even the bravest adventurerâ€™s stomach turn."]
	quest.0CE50A7F4F1A0E4D.quest_subtitle: "Find a Small Blimp"
	quest.0F77135D2BDD4E55.quest_desc: ["Gana 3 guerras de colonias como atacante."]
	quest.0F77135D2BDD4E55.quest_subtitle: "Gana 3 guerras atacando"
	quest.0F77135D2BDD4E55.title: "Conquistador"
	quest.14857DBF1DCBF100.quest_desc: ["Cresting the waves like a shadow of the past, this cursed vessel is crewed by skeletons that seem impossible to keep down. Every deck hides danger, every hold whispers of lost treasure and every strike you land may be fleeting. Only the bold (or the foolhardy) dare to face its relentless undead crew."]
	quest.14857DBF1DCBF100.quest_subtitle: "Find an Undead Pirate Ship"
	quest.1539EFED74FB2DCE.quest_desc: [
		"Has completado &aTODOS los hitos&r de la temporada de Arkcraft."
		""
		"&5Eres una Leyenda.&r Recibes el logro morado y el premio final."
	]
	quest.1539EFED74FB2DCE.quest_subtitle: "Completa todos los hitos"
	quest.1539EFED74FB2DCE.title: "Leyenda de Arkcraft"
	quest.188AAB5B74C6EAAE.quest_subtitle: "Discover an Infested Temple explorer map"
	quest.1A7C17E0977E2D98.quest_desc: ["Derrota un jefe en una Hot Zone de nivel 4 (BOMD)."]
	quest.1A7C17E0977E2D98.quest_subtitle: "Jefe de Hot Zone T4"
	quest.1A7C17E0977E2D98.title: "Cazador de Jefes (T4)"
	quest.1C375606107C117F.quest_subtitle: "Find Keep Kayra"
	quest.1CC09C5B65D64217.quest_desc: ["Mata 64 zombis y 64 esqueletos."]
	quest.1CC09C5B65D64217.quest_subtitle: "64 zombis y 64 esqueletos"
	quest.1CC09C5B65D64217.title: "Cazador de No-muertos"
	quest.1CCA31D9352C60E6.quest_desc: ["Clustered around a towering central â€œgrandmotherâ€ mushroom, these villages appear quaint from afar. Yet the villagers within are far more aggressive than their old-world counterparts, hiding a cunning fierceness beneath their colorful caps. Approach with caution as this village may welcome the unwary only to spring its traps."]
	quest.1CCA31D9352C60E6.quest_subtitle: "Find a mushroom village"
	quest.1CEF2A38948010A2.quest_desc: ["Out on the open seas, the &6Illagers&r have taken to the waves, commandeering massive galleys and swift corsairs. Their sails cast long shadows, and their cannons roar with fury. Only the bravest dare to board, for fortune favors those who seize it."]
	quest.1CEF2A38948010A2.quest_subtitle: "Find an Illager Corsair or an Illager Galley"
	quest.1F10BC33D22328BD.quest_desc: ["Time has claimed this once-sacred site, leaving its halls cracked and overgrown. Now, ghostly skeletons and trickster illusioners linger within, guarding little more than shadows of former glory. Though its dangers are real, the templeâ€™s sturdy walls make it a tempting refuge for those seeking a foothold in this hostile world."]
	quest.1F10BC33D22328BD.quest_subtitle: "Find an Abandoned Temple"
	quest.20C74F71420E9405.quest_desc: ["Coloca tu Ayuntamiento y funda tu primera colonia."]
	quest.20C74F71420E9405.quest_subtitle: "Funda tu colonia"
	quest.20C74F71420E9405.title: "Primer Pueblo"
	quest.21426F5EEC922866.quest_desc: ["Half-submerged in the oceans lie the petrified remains of a colossal beast, its skeletal form stretching farther than the eye can follow. Was it a creature of the deep, dragged ashore in ages pastâ€”or did it fall from the heavens themselves? No records remain, only questions carved into stone."]
	quest.21426F5EEC922866.quest_subtitle: "Find a Typhon"
	quest.24BC16B16D65BD5F.quest_desc: ["Invoca y derrota al Wither."]
	quest.24BC16B16D65BD5F.quest_subtitle: "Mata al Wither"
	quest.24BC16B16D65BD5F.title: "Pesadilla del Nether"
	quest.25EF5E22B01FE5BC.quest_desc: ["Sube los 8 edificios principales a nivel 5: Ayuntamiento, Universidad, Almacén, Constructor, Mina, Leñador, Granja y Pescador."]
	quest.25EF5E22B01FE5BC.quest_subtitle: "Los 8 edificios clave a nivel 5"
	quest.25EF5E22B01FE5BC.title: "Metrópolis"
	quest.26733BB163DCC344.quest_desc: ["Lleva tu Ayuntamiento al nivel máximo (5)."]
	quest.26733BB163DCC344.quest_subtitle: "Ayuntamiento a nivel 5"
	quest.26733BB163DCC344.title: "Capital"
	quest.2A0A01BE836BB2AB.quest_desc: ["A monument of grandeur and mystery, the Shiraz Palace sprawls in every direction, its halls twisting and turning beyond comprehension. Its purpose remains unknown, but its size and opulence are undeniable. Travelers beware: without a companion, itâ€™s all too easy to lose your way in this labyrinthine estate."]
	quest.2A0A01BE836BB2AB.quest_subtitle: "Find the Shiraz Palace"
	quest.2A1B0386B7987DD3.quest_desc: ["Vast and dreamlike, the Aviary stretches high into wtilight sky, its halls divided into four whimsical quadrants. Each one unfolds as a surreal sceneâ€”bright, strange, and perilous in its own way. To wander here feels like stepping beyond reality itself. Is this the journeyâ€™s endâ€¦ or just another beginning?"]
	quest.2A1B0386B7987DD3.quest_subtitle: "Find an Aviary"
	quest.2B70445E6CD99EDB.quest_desc: [
		"Strange structures have begun rising from the land. Mysterious dungeons, fortresses, and towers that pierce the skies. No one knows where they came from, only that theyâ€™re teeming with hostile creatures, forgotten treasures, and powerful secrets."
		""
		"Your task is to venture forth and uncover the mysteries of these ancient places. Each dungeon holds new dangers, but also the keys to survival: weapons, artifacts, and knowledge that will aid you in the trials ahead."
		""
		"Prepare yourself adventurer. &6Exploration&r and courage are the only ways to thrive in this world where the land itself rises against you."
	]
	quest.2DB4F395EA26DF4B.quest_subtitle: "Find a Coliseum"
	quest.2EFC5DBD8122A0AE.quest_desc: ["Far below the surface lies a twisted network of chambers, where the air is thick with disease and shadow. Once a place of treatment, it now resembles a burial ground for forgotten rulers, its halls echoing with the whispers of those long lost. Only the brave (or the desperate) dare to tread these haunted corridors."]
	quest.2EFC5DBD8122A0AE.quest_subtitle: "Find a Plague Asylum"
	quest.3182DC64ADB20D60.quest_desc: ["Gana 5 guerras de colonias como atacante."]
	quest.3182DC64ADB20D60.quest_subtitle: "Gana 5 guerras atacando"
	quest.3182DC64ADB20D60.title: "Señor de la Guerra"
	quest.3D1C0F80B74B27D5.quest_subtitle: "Arrive at a Lighthouse"
	quest.3ECA226F08D5195F.quest_desc: ["Hidden among hills and valleys, the monastery stands as a quiet refuge in a world of rising danger. Here, villagers tend to simple lives of prayer and work, untouched by Illager conquest. Though the halls hold little in the way of treasure, their sturdy walls and peaceful company make this an ideal sanctuary for weary adventurers."]
	quest.3ECA226F08D5195F.quest_subtitle: "Find a Monastery"
	quest.3F6697AF183E0B99.quest_desc: ["Gasta el total de la temporada en tributos: 191.400 CEV (los 8 edificios maxeados)."]
	quest.3F6697AF183E0B99.quest_subtitle: "Gasta todo: 191.400"
	quest.3F6697AF183E0B99.title: "Economía Dominada"
	quest.4118927D9D079DC8.quest_desc: ["Rising like jagged thorns from the ground, these massive towers are defended by skeletons entwined with deadly roses. Each level is heavily fortified, and flying rose guards patrol the skies above. Only those who ascend to the top will claim the treasures and secrets hidden within."]
	quest.4118927D9D079DC8.quest_subtitle: "Visit the Thornborn Towers"
	quest.436231715C11E3BA.quest_desc: ["Scattered across the wilds, small bands of Illagers set up camp beneath their distinctive purple tents. Though their supplies are meager and their loot scarce, their presence is a warning, the Illagersâ€™ reach grows wider with every outpost."]
	quest.436231715C11E3BA.quest_subtitle: "Find an Illager Campsite"
	quest.44D115281B0BFB75.quest_desc: ["Whispers speak of a &9flying vessel&r that hovers above the world, shimmering with strange energy. Few dare approach, for those who return tell of eerie lights, warped corridors, and guardians not of this realm. Seek it out, if you dareâ€”and uncover the secrets hidden within its metallic shell."]
	quest.44D115281B0BFB75.quest_subtitle: "Find a Giant Mushroom"
	quest.4791FC0A2E834D85.quest_desc: ["Dark magics linger in the depths of these dungeons, woven into items, halls, and even the very air. Power awaits the bold, but so do twisted fates for the careless."]
	quest.4791FC0A2E834D85.quest_subtitle: "Find a Bathhouse"
	quest.48F5F9351434F150.quest_desc: ["Derrota 300 monstruos."]
	quest.48F5F9351434F150.quest_subtitle: "Mata 300 monstruos"
	quest.48F5F9351434F150.title: "Exterminador"
	quest.4B2D5E4082A356DC.quest_desc: ["Gana tu primera guerra de colonias como atacante."]
	quest.4B2D5E4082A356DC.quest_subtitle: "Gana 1 guerra atacando"
	quest.4B2D5E4082A356DC.title: "Primera Sangre"
	quest.4E4052F7EAD4FDD6.quest_desc: ["Bright banners and painted walls lure travelers closer, but inside these towering strongholds, chaos reigns. Each floor brims with bandits and traps, their laughter echoing as waves of foes pour from endless spawners. Conquer the towers, and their richesâ€”and notorietyâ€”are yours."]
	quest.4E4052F7EAD4FDD6.quest_subtitle: "Find the Bandit Towers"
	quest.509E9CA83FBC780E.quest_subtitle: "Find a Fishing Hut"
	quest.5100CFAD43E7D67A.quest_desc: ["Rising like a monument to conquest, this sprawling fortress serves as a bastion of Illager power. Its many levels are patrolled by raiders and spellcasters, their banners declaring dominion over the land. Within its halls lie chambers of wealth, guarded by Evokers whose magic is as deadly as their stares."]
	quest.5100CFAD43E7D67A.quest_subtitle: "Find an Illager Fort"
	quest.53AF2B722A69DCDC.quest_desc: ["Tucked away in the tall grass, this lonely house stands weathered and broken, its timbers groaning with age. Easy to overlook, it bears little more than the memory of those who once called it home. Still, even the smallest refuge can hold a story."]
	quest.53AF2B722A69DCDC.quest_subtitle: "Find a Small Prairie House"
	quest.541BBC35DA4F0B73.quest_desc: ["Sprouting from a cluster of towering fungi, this outpost of miners has carved their livelihood into the surface world. Ruthless and territorial, they will defend their claim with tooth and nail. Whether the giant mushrooms shield them from the sun or serve some darker purpose, none can say. One truth remains certain: the mine runs rich with ore, for those bold enough to claim it."]
	quest.541BBC35DA4F0B73.quest_subtitle: "Find a Mushroom Mine"
	quest.5491E02F26DB3DFC.quest_desc: ["Gasta 100.000 CEV (~1.000 oro) en tributos."]
	quest.5491E02F26DB3DFC.quest_subtitle: "Gasta 100.000 en tributos"
	quest.5491E02F26DB3DFC.title: "Magnate"
	quest.5C00000000000001.quest_desc: ["Base rings craft at the table with free stats. Gem jewelry forged here. Uniques from HZ T4 boss."]
	quest.5C00000000000001.quest_subtitle: "Physical accessories - BC combat + ParCool"
